0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"之前有睇過下，如有暴動情況，日內瓦公約好似係不適用"},{"pid":"38e72192e2708c03e4a070c2e24cb13807f6e62e","tid":1468691,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d689cf0e1349dc54b363204a313dde99b26e2a","tid":1468691,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c74dcf6f47e3c0f627287c2b050b1df21ad8b67","tid":1468691,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"770fdbd3dcdfb31480f4bea79123b06d781e8537","tid":1468691,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201b75011f638a67eb497cb9118b816c11c5a5cd","tid":1468691,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:01:01.000Z","msg":"公安符合上述條件，但記者應該唔符合，因為有記者證。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:04:55.000Z","msg":"咁如果係個扮演記者嘅間諜呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:08:47.000Z","msg":"你證明到當你贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"香港係中國地方 中國處理間諜自古以來唔駛證明唔駛審訊<br />\n<br />\n中國處決30名美國間諜 <br />\n美國於2010年至2012年間，發生諜報系統重大意外，有約30名間諜被中國逮捕並處決。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2522101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2522101&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=8f2e8ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2522101&h=ea50d257\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2522101</a>"}]}